th the value observed by Papp\net al. [Phys. Rev. Lett. 101, 135301 (2008)]. Finally, we develop a\ndiagrammatic theory for the dynamic structure factor which accounts for the\ncorrelations beyond Bogoliubov theory and which covers the full range of\nmomenta and frequencies, showing the correct asymptotic scaling at large\nmomentum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2016 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2017 18:10:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-07"}
